name: ILLUMINATED - CHAPTER ONE: INFRASTRUCTURE - 'STORM'
description: “Illuminated” is a project I’ve been working on and thinking about for a couple years at this point. It is an expansive collection exploring nature, sci-fi, and realism. Using various ideas, I want to explore what the future would hold for the environment and how citizens of our future would live their lives. This is ‘STORM’, one of the first pieces in the collection. -Thomas
